{"tid":664881,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[經濟梁建芬]以叫雞一例支持Andrew Lo對短缺既見解","createTime":"2018-05-14T12:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T16:22:53.000Z","uid":40856,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b84b87679f08e5892203cd7385d9ebc381b83b0","tid":664881,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"Andrew 你真係傻鳩來 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講一堆野又搵教授都唔搵我幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就g持 雞奴既短缺下未必會出現非價格莖爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設而家有雞梁和雞奴一齊搵miki<br />\n咁大家都唔禮讓 要即時同miki做愛（短缺）<br />\n正常情況miki會梗係揀梁蛇啦 話晒老公丫嘛（非價格莖爭）<br />\n但miki竟然話：「我有兩個窿嘛，你地一場同事，一齊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n呢個例子證明市場會自己解決短缺，唔一定有非價格競爭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb07c6fd32f559f65e6f64894867ae9224d6a7e","tid":664881,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6b68eca53cc7149428d04112dd7cd57528bbb2","tid":664881,"uid":152520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b58e7bcc75cdccfdc8d45c291e466df66837fd","tid":664881,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f5dcd5b545c4023b6fdcea24d679260ee01490","tid":664881,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:43:31.000Z","msg":"無人對打我？"},{"pid":"a724fc4efa37ce2d08edf99537c4b9a2a54773ed","tid":664881,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:24:06.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈應該有比叫雞教授教過？"},{"